# Copy to simulation/.env and fill in <YOUR_API_KEY>. The Streamlit app
# reads this file at startup and falls back to a synthetic GBM dataset
# if no key is available.
#
# Get a free Graph Network API key:
#   1. https://thegraph.com/studio/apikeys/  → sign in with wallet
#   2. Create an API Key. Free tier is 100k queries/month.
#   3. When prompted for a billing chain, choose Arbitrum One — Ethereum
#      mainnet settlement was deprecated. This is independent of which
#      chain the subgraph indexes.
#
# Two options to point the app at a subgraph:
#
# Option A (recommended): just set GRAPH_API_KEY and let the code combine
# it with the default pool's deployment ID. The default pool is Uniswap
# v3 USDC/WETH 0.05% on Ethereum Mainnet, deployment ID
#   5zvR82QoaXYFyDEKLZ9t6v9adgnptxYpKpSbxtgVENFV
# (Source: developers.uniswap.org/docs/ecosystem/subgraphs/overview)
#
# GRAPH_API_KEY=your_key_here
#
# Option B: set the full URL explicitly (e.g. to query a different chain).
#
# SUBGRAPH_URL=https://gateway.thegraph.com/api/<YOUR_API_KEY>/subgraphs/id/5zvR82QoaXYFyDEKLZ9t6v9adgnptxYpKpSbxtgVENFV
